CONCERN is growing for a teenager who vanished from his Glasgow home.Thanh Van Bui was last seen at around 7.45am on Friday.Police said the 15-year-old lives in Pollokshields and officers are carrying out inquiries in a bid to find him.Thanh is described as 5ft 4in tall and of slim build, with short dark hair.When last seen he was wearing a black jacket, grey zipper top, jeans and grey trainers.Inspector Alan Scullion, from Cathcart Police Office, said: &quot;Police enquiries are ongoing to trace Thanh.&quot;I would urge anyone who may have seen him or who has any information on his whereabouts to contact Police Scotland on 101.&quot;